cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.MM 

The paper deals with large-scale visual search, recommendation, clustering, and deduplication using hashing-based matching. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of a graph-based clustering algorithm, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and database (cs.DB) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with image collections, which suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
